  "description": "The initiation of the coral colony — the first polyp settling and beginning to build. Pulse src1 at default tuning against Saw src2 detuned +3 semitones, slight detune that creates a slow beating between the two. proc1=LP (2400 Hz, low reso 0.2) — Pulse stays bright; proc2=LP (820 Hz, reso 0.38) — Saw is more firmly contained. fmDepth=0.12 is minimal; the collision is more harmonic than FM-driven. srcMix=0.42 favours the Pulse slightly. Clean poly4 voicing: multiple polyps stacking. Env->FilterCutoff, LFO->WavetablePos (inactive but future-wired), Velocity->Volume, Aftertouch->Pan. Poly8 for full coral colony stacking.",
  "tags": ["obrix", "foundation", "pulse", "saw", "constructive-collision", "coral", "first", "polyp"],
